cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the application of deep neural networks for MRI reconstruction, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of transfer learning is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also involves medical imaging (cs.MM) as it deals with MRI reconstruction.
